          "id": "0334d27b025d3dfe7e99bb6676ed6cf0ca680c64",
          "message": "Narrow WebGL context type in YUV renderer\n\nRename the initial WebGL context variable to glCtx and, after the null check, reassign it to const gl: WebGLRenderingContext. This ensures TypeScript sees a non-null WebGLRenderingContext (useful inside closures) and avoids union-type issues; also adds a brief explanatory comment.",
          "timestamp": "2026-03-08T15:20:08-04:00",
          "tree_id": "2af52fe1f83a221565d5de5b327cf6ce5ac37178",
