          "distinct": true,
          "id": "1f1f25ae49eccb4c488c96300e696ccda86729aa",
          "message": "events: Add SCTE-104 and MXL data flow support\n\nAdd end-to-end support for discrete MXL data/ancillary flows and SCTE-104 integration. Introduces DataGrain and NewDataReader with a dataLoop, source-level OnDataGrain callback and dataFanOut, and writer-side dataRef/SetDataWriter/WriteDataGrain plus Output.StartLifecycle accepting an optional data writer. Application wiring updated: MXL source specs can include a data flow id, app opens data flows, parses ST291/SCTE-104 payloads and forwards cues into the SCTE-35 injector; initSCTE104 wires injector output to encode/wrap SCTE-104 and write data grains. Adds --scte104 flag and exposes SCTE-104 enabled state in control API. Extensive tests added for reader/source/writer data paths and new scte104 package files for encode/decode/translation.",
          "timestamp": "2026-03-09T13:31:25-04:00",
          "tree_id": "75c02e419576e98f9163a28e23771db582719a6d",
          "url": "https://github.com/zsiec/switchframe/commit/1f1f25ae49eccb4c488c96300e696ccda86729aa"
